definitions.definition: A place in the United States :

subdefinitions.definition: A town in Lee County , Arkansas .

definitions.definition: A hamlet in Lacombe County , central Alberta , Canada , named after Haynes Creek .
A village and civil parish in Central Bedfordshire district, Bedfordshire , England ( OS grid ref TL0942 ) .
A suburb of Perth , in the City of Armadale , Western Australia .
